pullRequest.body:
We formalize the proof by Grothendieck that abelian categories which have exact filtering colimits and a generator have enough injectives (*Sur quelques points d'algèbre homologique*, Tôhoku Mathematical Journal 9, 1957).

---

- [x] depends on: #19306
- [x] depends on: #19992
- [x] depends on: #19935
- [ ] depends on: #20157
- [ ] depends on: #20014
- [ ] depends on: #20146
